{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Lazy Nyaong"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9f530d33-4d29-53fe-b233-574054b276c8","excerpt":"APIs에 대하여 documentation, URLs, Payloads, Authentication, Authorization, Errors, Caching를 주제로 각각의 The good, The bad, The ugly 케이스를 얘기한다. Documentation The Good…","html":"<p><div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.42857142857143%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem\" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/t0nl5aUfAvY?rel=0\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div> </div></p>\n<p>APIs에 대하여 documentation, URLs, Payloads, Authentication, Authorization, Errors, Caching를 주제로 각각의 The good, The bad, The ugly 케이스를 얘기한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"documentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#documentation\" aria-label=\"documentation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Documentation</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The Good: It Exists</li>\n<li>The Bad: Not up to date</li>\n<li>The Ugly: Where is the documentation?</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"urls\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#urls\" aria-label=\"urls permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>URLs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The Good: <strong>Consistency</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>if it respects REST Conventions</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  /users/22445\n  /products/3156\n  /movies/127/times</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>The Bad: Inconsistency</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  /users/22445\n  /reviews/3156  &lt;== Not review or time id&#39;s\n  /times/127</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>The Ugly:</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  GET /remove  &lt;==used GET method to delete something</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"payloads\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#payloads\" aria-label=\"payloads permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Payloads</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The Good</p>\n<ul>\n<li>하나의 Endpoint에 필요한 모든 데이터가 있는 경우</li>\n<li>Content-Type을 잘 지키는 경우</li>\n<li>Versioning이 필요할 때 하는 경우 (그렇지 않을 경우, 어느 순간 Breaking change로 인해 payload에 변동이 있을 경우 client는 고장난다)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Bad</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>같은 값에 대해 Endpoint마다 다른 property로 전달하는 경우</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Endpoint</th>\n<th>“id” field</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>/products</td>\n<td>id</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>/products/:id</td>\n<td>productID</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>/cart</td>\n<td>product_id</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>(이런 경우는 나도 자주 봤는데, 특히 각각의 Endpoint를 개발한 사람이 다른 경우 발생하기 쉽다.)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Payload가 자주 변하는 경우: 이미지의 경로가 <a href=\"http://images~\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://images~</a> 였는데 암묵적으로 http:// 를 빠지게 되어서 client에서 이미지가 나오지 않게 되었다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Ugly</p>\n<ul>\n<li>JSON containing HTML | XML containing HTML</li>\n<li>Unstable: </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"authentication-who-are-you\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#authentication-who-are-you\" aria-label=\"authentication who are you permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Authentication: Who are you?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The Good</p>\n<ul>\n<li>SSL</li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/ssl-pinning/\">SSL Pinning</a></li>\n<li>OAuth</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Bad</p>\n<ul>\n<li>OAuth (she says OAuth is very controversial)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>The Ugly: 직접 다 만드는 경우</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"authorization-what-are-you-allowed-to-do\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#authorization-what-are-you-allowed-to-do\" aria-label=\"authorization what are you allowed to do permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Authorization: What are you allowed to do?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The Good</p>\n<ul>\n<li>App Requests Permissions\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.515337423312886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Google Cloud Storage JSON API, v1\"\n        title=\"Google Cloud Storage JSON API, v1\"\n        src=\"/static/457cdb7f5119b90ab3266b8bbddd9539/a6d36/authorization.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/457cdb7f5119b90ab3266b8bbddd9539/222b7/authorization.png 163w,\n/static/457cdb7f5119b90ab3266b8bbddd9539/ff46a/authorization.png 325w,\n/static/457cdb7f5119b90ab3266b8bbddd9539/a6d36/authorization.png 650w,\n/static/457cdb7f5119b90ab3266b8bbddd9539/e548f/authorization.png 975w,\n/static/457cdb7f5119b90ab3266b8bbddd9539/5b587/authorization.png 1010w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>The Bad: A Single Api Key => 키가 탈취당할 경우 </li>\n<li>The Ugly: Authorization? 만약 Authentication(인증)만 있고 그걸로 모든 권한을 준다면, 결국 어딘가 잘못될 것이다.\n모바일 앱이라고 해도 Charles(Web Debugging Proxy) 같은 HTTP debugger로 해킹은 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"errors\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#errors\" aria-label=\"errors permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Errors</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The Good</p>\n<ul>\n<li>proper HTTP status code</li>\n<li>error message in response</li>\n<li>human readable error message</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Bad</p>\n<ul>\n<li>messages like “There was an error” => 불친절한 메시지</li>\n<li>status code는 200인데, error code를 response body에 담는 경우</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Ugly</p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTML page를 return하는 경우</li>\n<li>404 page를 200 code와 함께 return하는 경우</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"caching\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#caching\" aria-label=\"caching permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Caching</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The Good</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Using one of the standards</li>\n<li>Cache-Control</li>\n<li>etags</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Bad</p>\n<ul>\n<li>no caching but Manually processing data</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>The Ugly: cache? i don’t care</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"trdl\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#trdl\" aria-label=\"trdl permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>TR;DL</h1>\n<h3 id=\"whats-needed-in-your-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#whats-needed-in-your-api\" aria-label=\"whats needed in your api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What’s needed in your API</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Consistency</li>\n<li>Conventions</li>\n<li>Simple</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"qa\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#qa\" aria-label=\"qa permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Q&#x26;A</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>api endpoint의 versioning에 대해 선호하는 방법: Path로 버전을 설정하는 걸 좋아한다. header나 date를 가지고 versioning을 할 수도 있을 것이다.</li>\n<li>HTTP2를 사용해도 여러개의 Api를 합쳐서 하나로 만들 필요가 있을까? (payload에서 the good에 해당하는 질문): 여러개의 api를 호출하면 그 중 하나는 실패할 수 있다. 그게 서버상의 문제일 수도 있고 인터넷 환경에 의한 경우일 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#documentation\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#urls\">URLs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#payloads\">Payloads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#authentication-who-are-you\">Authentication: Who are you?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#authorization-what-are-you-allowed-to-do\">Authorization: What are you allowed to do?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#errors\">Errors</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#caching\">Caching</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#trdl\">TR;DL</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#whats-needed-in-your-api\">What’s needed in your API</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/#qa\">Q&#x26;A</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"APIs: The Good, The Bad, The Ugly","date":"September 04, 2019","description":"Techlahoma 200 OK 2019 행사에서 Michele Titolo의 발표","category":"study","creator":null,"created_at":null,"link":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/study/APIs-The-Good-The-Bad-The-Ugly/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/study/ssl-pinning/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[번역] SSL Pinning","category":"study"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2718815002","452372368","63159454"]}